<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>بِبِلَادِ خُرَاسَانَ فَهَزَمَهُمْ مُوسَى بْنُ بُغَا هَزِيمَةً فَظِيعَةً.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَفِيهَا كَانَتْ وَقْعَةٌ بَيْنَ مَسْرُورٍ الْبَلْخِيِّ وَبَيْنَ مَسَاوِرٍ الْخَارِجِيِّ، فَأَسَرَ مَسْرُورٌ مِنْ أَصْحَابِهِ جَمَاعَةً كَثِيرَةً.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَفِيهَا حَجَّ بِالنَّاسِ الْفَضْلُ بْنُ إِسْحَاقَ الْمُتَقَدِّمُ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">وَمِمَّنْ تُوُفِّيَ فِيهَا مِنَ الْأَعْيَانِ:</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>أَحْمَدُ بْنُ بُدَيْلٍ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَأَحْمَدُ بْنُ حَفْصٍ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وَأَحْمَدُ بْنُ سِنَانٍ الْقَطَّانُ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>وَأَحْمَدُ بْنُ الْفُرَاتِ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>وَحَمِيدُ بْنُ الرَّبِيعِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>وَمُحَمَّدُ بْنُ سَنْجَرَ، صَاحِبُ الْمُسْنَدِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَمُحَمَّدُ بْنُ يَحْيَى الذُّهْلِيُّ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>وَيَحْيَى بْنُ مُعَاذٍ الرَّازِيُّ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>